---
source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: css/selectors/line_comments/selector-boundary-comments.css
---

# Input

```css
.a
// before +
+
// after +
.b
// before block
{color:red}

.a// before +
+.b{color:orange}

.a+// after +
.b{color:purple}

.before// keep with >
>.middle+.after{color:navy}

.before>// keep after >
.middle+.after{color:teal}

.before>.middle// keep with +
+.after{color:maroon}

.before
// descendant
.middle+.after{color:olive}

```


# Options

```json
{
  "css": {
    "parser": {
      "allowWrongLineComments": true
    }
  }
}
```

# Formatted

```css
.a
// before +
+
// after +
.b
// before block
{
	color: red;
}

.a // before +
+ .b {
	color: orange;
}

.a + // after +
.b {
	color: purple;
}

.before // keep with >
> .middle + .after {
	color: navy;
}

.before > // keep after >
.middle + .after {
	color: teal;
}

.before > .middle // keep with +
+ .after {
	color: maroon;
}

.before
// descendant
.middle + .after {
	color: olive;
}

```
